The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques applied to customer reviews for answering specific queries about products. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
